Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別篇  其之二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱～  好熱～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（啪嗒）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是需要幫忙啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我把我的段郎人偶送給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Miya Raphael Miya）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我努力寫成的詩送給你～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:57.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Gabriel Saya）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:02.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Lucifer Do Tama）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把…Blade Braver的DVD…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:06.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Kirino Michael）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把不好的水…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾在這些當中你只能選一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…這不好的水…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我來晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:20.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東  你好慢啊        又搞錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:20.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:23.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}咦  已經結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之是得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊！力量不斷湧出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  真是傻瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點不假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那水凡人就是沒法控制嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼～是夢嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
